                "# Latent Altruism: Steering Cooperative Intent in LLMs\n",
                "## NeurIPS 2026 - Reproducibility Notebook\n",
                "\n",
                "This notebook contains the complete, end-to-end execution pipeline for the 4 novel experiments presented in the paper:\n",
                "1. **Veto Circuit Analysis (Mechanistic Interpretability)**\n",
                "2. **Sparse Autoencoder Steering**\n",
                "3. **Theory of Mind (Trust) Steering**\n",
                "4. **Dynamic Steering (Conditional Reciprocity)**\n",
                "\n",
                "It also includes the **Reviewer-Ready Deep Analytics**: Perplexity Calculation (Capabilities Preservation), Layer Sweeps (Strategic Bottleneck), and Control Vector Ablation."
            ]
        },
        {
